definitions.definition: Of two things: that cannot coexist ; not congruous because of differences ; unable to function together due to dissimilarities.
examples: My phone is incompatible with the latest version of this app.

definitions.definition: Incapable of being together without mutual reaction or decomposition , as certain medicines.
